  "detailed_description": "<i>COLD DEPTH is a first person survival horror game about exploring underwater stations in the near future.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/6b4e706594f4d8e115df63cc5112d8cc.poster.avif?t=1755354529\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/6b4e706594f4d8e115df63cc5112d8cc.webm?t=1755354529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/6b4e706594f4d8e115df63cc5112d8cc.mp4?t=1755354529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>EVERYTHING WENT WRONG</strong><br>The year is 2030. In the Black Sea, due to a record increase in water salinity and strange oxygen emissions, a lot of minerals have been found.<br>It is here, in the Black Sea at a depth of two thousand meters, that there is an underwater complex - \"Oasis\",<br>It was recently built by the independent corporation \"AO\" (\"Atlantic Union\"), which is engaged in the extraction, purification and supply of minerals from the seabed.<br><br>The main character Lisa goes to work at a drilling station, but everything went wrong. Whether she will survive or die depends only on you. Save her.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/a7860332e8c717b96cffa57a4b29d212.poster.avif?t=1755354529\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/a7860332e8c717b96cffa57a4b29d212.webm?t=1755354529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/a7860332e8c717b96cffa57a4b29d212.mp4?t=1755354529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stations power management.<br></li><li>Physics-based interactions. 90% Objects in the game are physics interactive.<br></li><li>Recycling, 3D Printing and Packing objects in movable inventory.<br></li><li>Character parameters and effects.<br></li><li>Replacing broken parts with new ones (printed on our 3d printers).</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>COLD DEPTH is a first person survival horror game about exploring underwater stations in the near future.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/6b4e706594f4d8e115df63cc5112d8cc.poster.avif?t=1755354529\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/6b4e706594f4d8e115df63cc5112d8cc.webm?t=1755354529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/6b4e706594f4d8e115df63cc5112d8cc.mp4?t=1755354529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>EVERYTHING WENT WRONG</strong><br>The year is 2030. In the Black Sea, due to a record increase in water salinity and strange oxygen emissions, a lot of minerals have been found.<br>It is here, in the Black Sea at a depth of two thousand meters, that there is an underwater complex - \"Oasis\",<br>It was recently built by the independent corporation \"AO\" (\"Atlantic Union\"), which is engaged in the extraction, purification and supply of minerals from the seabed.<br><br>The main character Lisa goes to work at a drilling station, but everything went wrong. Whether she will survive or die depends only on you. Save her.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/a7860332e8c717b96cffa57a4b29d212.poster.avif?t=1755354529\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/a7860332e8c717b96cffa57a4b29d212.webm?t=1755354529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/a7860332e8c717b96cffa57a4b29d212.mp4?t=1755354529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stations power management.<br></li><li>Physics-based interactions. 90% Objects in the game are physics interactive.<br></li><li>Recycling, 3D Printing and Packing objects in movable inventory.<br></li><li>Character parameters and effects.<br></li><li>Replacing broken parts with new ones (printed on our 3d printers).</li></ul>",
